'''天主教金沙薩總教區'''（{{lang-la|Archidioecesis Kinshasana}}；{{lang-fr|Archidiocèse de Kinshasa}}）是[[羅馬天主教|羅馬天主教]]一個[[總教區|總教區]]，下轄8個教區。

總教區管轄[[剛果民主共和國|剛果民主共和國]]首都[[金沙薩|金沙薩]]以及[[班頓杜省|班頓杜省]]位於[[剛果河|剛果河]]和[[開賽河|開賽河]]之間的地區，2006年時有3,601,000名教友，佔轄區總人口50.0%。教區下轄125個[[堂區|堂區]]，有1,038名[[司鐸|司鐸]]。現任總主教為{{link-en|弗里多蘭·昂邦戈-貝桑居|Fridolin Ambongo Besungu}}[[樞機|樞機]]<ref>{{cite web |title=AMBONGO BESUNGU Card. Fridolin, O.F.M. Cap. |url=https://press.vatican.va/content/salastampa/en/documentation/cardinali_biografie/cardinali_bio_Ambongo.html |publisher=Holy See Press Office |accessdate=2020-06-30 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20200630112017/https://press.vatican.va/content/salastampa/en/documentation/cardinali_biografie/cardinali_bio_Ambongo.html |archivedate=2020-06-30 |language=en |dead-url=no }}</ref>，輔理主教為{{link-de|愛德華·基松加-恩丁加|Edouard Kisonga Ndinga|愛德華·基松加}}、{{link-de|若望-克利斯本·基姆貝尼-基-康達|Jean-Crispin Kimbeni Ki Kanda}}、{{link-de|雲先·特松巴-桑巴-科特索|Vincent Tshomba Shamba Kotsho}}和{{link-de|嘉祿·恩達卡-薩拉比薩拉|Charles Ndaka Salabisala}}<ref>{{cite press release |title=Le Udienze, 11.09.2014 |url=https://press.vatican.va/content/salastampa/it/bollettino/pubblico/2014/09/11/0624/01393.html |publisher=Sala Stampa della Santa Sede |accessdate=2020-06-30 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20200630114416/https://press.vatican.va/content/salastampa/it/bollettino/pubblico/2014/09/11/0624/01393.html |archivedate=2020-06-30 |language=it |date=2014-09-11 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite press release |title=Resignations and Appointments, 29.06.2020 |url=https://press.vatican.va/content/salastampa/en/bollettino/pubblico/2020/06/29/200629b.html |publisher=Holy See Press Office |accessdate=2020-06-30 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20200630055829/https://press.vatican.va/content/salastampa/en/bollettino/pubblico/2020/06/29/200629b.html |archivedate=2020-06-30 |language=en |date=2020-06-29 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，榮休總主教為[[老楞佐·蒙森沃·帕辛亞|老楞佐·蒙森沃·帕辛亞]]樞機<ref>{{cite press release |title=Resignations and Appointments, 01.11.2018 |url=https://press.vatican.va/content/salastampa/en/bollettino/pubblico/2018/11/01/181101c.html |publisher=Holy See Press Office |accessdate=2019-07-17 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20190717061440/https://press.vatican.va/content/salastampa/en/bollettino/pubblico/2018/11/01/181101c.html |archivedate=2019-07-17 |language=en |date=2018-11-01 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

[[比屬剛果|比屬剛果]][[自治傳教團|自治傳教團]]於1886年11月22日成立，1888年5月11日升為'''利奧波德維爾宗座代牧區'''，1959年11月10日升為總教區<ref>{{cite book |title=ACTA APOSTOLICAE SEDIS |series=III |volume=II |year=1960 |publisher=Typis Polyglottis Vaticanis |pages=372-377 |url=https://www.vatican.va/archive/aas/documents/AAS-52-1960-ocr.pdf |accessdate=2020-04-17 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20200417100439/https://www.vatican.va/archive/aas/documents/AAS-52-1960-ocr.pdf |archivedate=2020-04-17 |language=la |dead-url=no }}</ref>，1966年5月30日易名至今。

